author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Paylocity Reports Q2 EPS $0.16
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - Paylocity Holding Corp:
* PAYLOCITY ANNOUNCES SECOND QUARTER FISCAL YEAR 2018 FINANCIAL RESULTS
* Q2 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.16 * Q2 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.01 * Q2 REVENUE ROSE 25 PERCENT TO $86 MILLION * SEES Q3 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.45 TO $0.47 * SEES FY 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.87 TO $0.89 * SEES FY 2018 REVENUE $369 MILLION TO $371 MILLION * SEES Q3 2018 REVENUE $110 MILLION TO $111 MILLION * Q2 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.12, REVENUE VIEW $85.0 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q3 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.46, REVENUE VIEW $110.5 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* FY2018 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.86, REVENUE VIEW $370.2 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
